<paragraph blockId="18.[685,1172,1629,1729]" pageId="18">
The six species in this group have the elytral punctures end before the elytral apex. The combined distribution of these species extends from 
<collectingCountry box="[685,777,1708,1729]" name="Honduras" pageId="18">Honduras</collectingCountry>
to 
<collectingCountry box="[812,885,1708,1729]" name="Bolivia" pageId="18">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
